               <msContents>
                  <summary/>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="5r" to="137v">Fols 5r–137v</locus>
                     <title>Horologion for the night ሰዐታት ፡ ዘሌሊት</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሃሌ፡ ሉያ፡ አአትብ፡ ወእትነሣእ፡ በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፫አስማተ፡ ነሢእየ፡ እትመረጐዝ፡</incipit>
                     <note>                     Introductory prayer, fol. 5r-9r; Scriptural readings, fol. 9r-17v; Principal prayer, fol. 17v-31v; Scriptural readings, fol. 31v-41v; Scriptural readings for the hours of the night, fol. 42r-91r; Prayer and scriptural readings for the hours of the day, fol. 91r-137v
                     </note>
                     <notatedMusic><desc>Partially supplied with musical notation</desc></notatedMusic>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
