                                                        </origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>Copied perhaps for አሚነ፡ ክርስቶስ Anima Krestos (prayer, fol. 1v, 4rv, 136r) and ወልደ፡ ዮሐንስ Walda Yohannes (prayer, fol. 2v, 136r). Purchased by ቄሰ፡ ገበዝ፡ ወልደ፡ አማኑኤል Qēsa Gabaz Walda Amānu'ēl from መምሬ፡ ወልደ፡ መድኅን Mammerē Walda Madhen for Makāna Śellāsē church, f. 137v. In Holy Trinity Cathedral when filmed.</provenance>
               </history>
